37090>>>>>    
37090>>>>>    
37090>>>>>    //
37090>>>>>    // This procedure is called when validating a session and after logging in. Its purpose is to 
37090>>>>>    // update properties based on the session and user data. Augment this function to update 
37090>>>>>    // properties based on the session / user table. Note that WebAppUser and WebAppSession contain
37090>>>>>    // the right records when this procedure is called.
37090>>>>>    //
37090>>>>>    // Params:
37090>>>>>    //      bClear   True if the procedure is called before session validation to clear properties.
37090>>>>>    //
37090>>>>>    Procedure UpdateSessionProperties Boolean bClear
37092>>>>>        Handle hoUserDD
37092>>>>>        
37092>>>>>        Get phoUserDD to hoUserDD
37093>>>>>        
37093>>>>>        //  Update user properties
37093>>>>>        If (not(bClear) and HasRecord(hoUserDD)) Begin
37095>>>>>            Set psUsername to (Trim(WebAppUser.FullName))
37096>>>>>            Set psLoginName to (Trim(WebAppUser.LoginName))
37097>>>>>            Set piUserRights to WebAppUser.Rights
37098>>>>>            
37098>>>>>            Send OnSessionPropertiesSet 
37099>>>>>        End
37099>>>>>>
37099>>>>>        Else Begin
37100>>>>>            Set psUsername to ""
37101>>>>>            Set psLoginName to ""
37102>>>>>            Set piUserRights to 0
37103>>>>>            
37103>>>>>            Send OnSessionPropertiesClear
37104>>>>>        End
37104>>>>>>
37104>>>>>    End_Procedure
37105>>>>>    
37105>>>>>    Procedure OnSessionPropertiesSet
37107>>>>>        //  Empty event stub
37107>>>>>    End_Procedure
37108>>>>>    
37108>>>>>    Procedure OnSessionPropertiesClear
37110>>>>>        //  Empty event stub
37110>>>>>    End_Procedure
37111>>>>>    
37111>>>>>    Procedure EndSession
37113>>>>>        Integer iErr
37113>>>>>        Boolean bLogWebSession
37113>>>>>        Handle hoSessionDD       
37113>>>>>        
37113>>>>>        Get phoSessionDD to hoSessionDD
37114>>>>>        Get pbLogWebSession to bLogWebSession
37115>>>>>        If not bLogWebSession Begin
37117>>>>>            Forward Send EndSession
37119>>>>>            Procedure_Return
37120>>>>>        End
37120>>>>>>
37120>>>>>            
37120>>>>>        //  Check if session exists
37120>>>>>        Send Clear of hoSessionDD
37121>>>>>        Get psSessionKey to WebAppSession.SessionKey
37122>>>>>        
37122>>>>>        Send Find of hoSessionDD EQ Index.1
37123>>>>>        If (Found) Begin
37125>>>>>            Set Field_Changed_Value of hoSessionDD Field WebAppSession.Active to "N"
37126>>>>>            Get Request_Validate of hoSessionDD to iErr
37127>>>>>            If (iErr) Begin
37129>>>>>                // this should not happen. If it does its a programming error
37129>>>>>                Error DFERR_PROGRAM C_$WebAppSessionValidateFailed
37130>>>>>>
37130>>>>>                Procedure_Return
37131>>>>>            End
37131>>>>>>
37131>>>>>            Send Request_Save of hoSessionDD
37132>>>>>        End
37132>>>>>>
37132>>>>>    End_Procedure
37133>>>>>
37133>>>>>End_Class
37134>>>>>
